                  </hi>. I am single, and live at 25, Houndsditch. On Saturday evening, about a quarter past seven o'clock, I was in Houndsditch—I had a purse containing three half-crowns, and eight shillings—I missed the weight, turned, and saw a boy about the prisoner's height running—I followed—my purse has not been found—this is one of my shillings—(<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>)—it has "L" on it.</p>
